{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Now available:\u00a0 Blitz Mode!</strong>\u00a0 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This new Roguelite mode features procedural\u00a0battles\u00a0and\u00a0rewards.\u00a0 It is designed\u00a0to\u00a0be heavily replayable, challenging,\u00a0and\u00a0satisfying.\u00a0 Gain game breaking positive and negative perks as you fight against a variety of monsters pulled from Story Mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174030/extras/blitzCoverImage.png?t=1727715780\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After an accident the protagonist wakes up outside a mysterious lodge: inside the Hero Lodge they are tasked with protecting the land, with the promise of redemption for those who do a good job. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174030/extras/justLodge.png?t=1727715780\" />Embark on missions spanning 5 separate campaigns (and if so desired, 5 NG+ versions of those campaigns with altered  and more challenging enemies).  Hero Lodge has a minimalist story and isn't bogged down by page after page of dialogue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Equip heroes from a wide array of weapons and accessories to be strong enough to face your foes.  Optional crafting systems help you to create new weapons and accessories.  There are over 150 different weapons and over 200 accessories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174030/extras/weaponScrollGif2.gif?t=1727715780\" />Level heroes up to increase their Strength, Agility, Faith, or Magic.  Different heroes and weapons scale with different statistics.  There is a level cap to help maintain balanced game play and prevent the need for excessive grinding.  As your team rank increases, by beating missions for the first time, the level cap will raise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemies will behave in learnable ways:  figure out how to avoid or mitigate their skills and attacks.  Some enemies will just try to attack whatever is closest, some will focus on whomever has dealt them the most damage, and so on. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174030/extras/ratcutGifBlock.gif?t=1727715780\" />Create your party from a pool of up to 25 unique heroes that each have unique skills.  You'll unlock more heroes as you increase your team rank.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174030/extras/heroesInLine.png?t=1727715780\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your choices matter:  as you play through the game you'll be given several choices that will effect things yet to come including influencing what ending you get.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle against 50 unique enemies.  View detailed stats and descriptions for the enemies you've battled in the Bestiary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174030/extras/bestiaryBookOpen.gif?t=1727715780\" />Hero Lodge was created by a Solo Developer including all art and music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174030/extras/wolfShamanWolfUp.gif?t=1727715780\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to the Hero Lodge","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1174030/2c04ba67b695eb34feb0901b4148e54d5059de67.jpg"},{"name":"Team Rank 10","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1174030/67b3c714e5944987de0bcb43f5e2357fe09